{"tid":1867192,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"係咪急需一場支持罷工大遊行？","createTime":"2020-02-07T05:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T06:00:24.000Z","uid":41005,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4811359750e4e48e6f268f3e4faf7e00e627c90","tid":1867192,"uid":41005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比政府 比全球 睇下香港人既決心<br />\n<br />\n雖然要浪費一個口罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37d509d49f53ef9655ff393346bb5282f4c0945","tid":1867192,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:35:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fed84a7b70d7bd3d03b12fe611ecc2dd0ec838a","tid":1867192,"uid":41005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"罷工 封關 政府無能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7e7cb3e925ab0d95e533b7cde664710047f9d2","tid":1867192,"uid":35256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf8213491f5d28d260de0120ecbae103d3d138de","tid":1867192,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"其實而家大家不斷話enjoy home office<br />\n話home office咪即係同罷工一樣<br />\n其實咁咪就係中咗政府圈套囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講你Home Office即係繼續提供生產力<br />\n可能隨時仲做得多過平時 <br />\n因為你要係屋企長時間on call<br />\n但係本身三罷就係要影響經濟甚至攬炒<br />\n所以依家根本完全違背三罷原意<br />\n<br />\n所以就算將來你個界別話要罷工<br />\n但如果公司其實要你變相繼續home office<br />\n咁就即係等於冇用<br />\n<br />\n支持醫護 全港三罷大行動<br />\n就算成功三罷 都要留意執行方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1849793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1849793</a>"}]}